'''''Virunga''''' ni filime documentaire yo mu Bwongereza yakinwe muri 2014 iyobowe na Orlando von Einsiedel<ref>https://www.rocoeducational.com/virunga</ref> . Yibanze ku bikorwa byo kubungabunga abashinzwe parike muri pariki ya [[Pariki y’Ibirunga ya Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Virunga ya]] [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Kongo]] mu gihe havutse imyigaragambyo ikaze ya M23 mu mwaka wa 2012<ref>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com/films/reviews/view/27525/virunga</ref>, kandi ikora iperereza ku bikorwa by’isosiyete ikora peteroli yo mu Bwongereza Soco International mu murage ndangamurage wa UNESCO<ref>https://variety.com/2020/film/news/leonardo-dicaprio-barry-jenkins-virunga-1234646865/</ref>.  Soco International yarangije gushakisha peteroli muri Virunga muri Mata 2014<ref>https://www.indiewire.com/2014/11/review-virunga-will-change-your-perspective-on-the-crisis-in-congo-68395/</ref>.  Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Tribeca ku ya 17 Mata 2014<ref>https://www.un.org/en/ccoi/virunga-screening</ref>. Nyuma yo gutambuka kuri Netflix, yatorewe igihembo cya Akademiki ya Best Documentary Feature <ref>https://www.filmplatform.net/product/virunga/</ref>.<ref>https://berthafoundation.org/story/virunga-impact-report-2/</ref>
