=== Ibihembo ===
''Virunga'' yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi harimo na Peabody Award .<ref>https://africasacountry.com/2015/04/virunga-is-an-important-film-even-if-it-doesnt-preference-perspectives-from-local-stakeholders</ref> Feature documentaire Award ku DOXA documentaire Festival mu Vancouver, Canada; igihembo cy'umukinnyi mpuzamahanga wavutse muri Hot Docs i Toronto<ref>https://www.africanews.com/2021/07/01/climate-activists-oppose-oil-exploration-call-for-a-fossil-free-virunga-in-new-film//</ref>; Igihembo cya Zahabu ya Rock mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime Ntoya<ref>https://whc.unesco.org/en/news/1265</ref>; n'Ibikorwa no Guhinduka Hamwe (ACT Now) Igihembo cya Crested Butte Film Festival . Yatsindiye gongs ebyiri muri One World Media Awards muri BAFTA - Inyandiko nziza<ref>https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/movies/barry-jenkins-leonardo-dicaprio-netflix-partner-for-feature-adaptation-of-virunga/article31904298.ece</ref>, . Iyi filime kandi yatorewe igihembo cyiza cya Documentaire nziza muri Tribeca Film Festival.  Filime yatorewe igihembo cya Akademiki kubera ibihembo bya Documentaire Nziza ya 87 ya Osama Awards <ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/07/movies/virunga-a-searing-documentary-set-in-congo.html</ref>.

